RESOLVED that the Chicago Teachers Union (CTU) will send a letter to the US ambassador to Bahrain, and to Shaikh Kalid bin Ali al Khalifa of the Bahraini Ministry of Justice and Islamic Affairs calling for the release of Madhi Issa Madhi Abu Dheeb, and respect for democratic rights, like the freedom of speech, in Bahrain and,
Take up a collection at this HOD meeting to help with legal defense for the Bahraini teachers union leader, and
Send a letter of solidarity to Madhi Issa Madhi Abu Dheeb and his family to accompany any funds we were able to raise.